4:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-invert prose-lg max-w-none mb-16 [&_h2]:font-extrabold [&_h2]:tracking-tight [&_h2]:text-foreground [&_h2]:mt-12 [&_h2]:mb-4 [&_h3]:font-bold [&_h3]:text-foreground [&_h3]:mt-8 [&_h3]:mb-3 [&_p]:text-muted-foreground [&_p]:leading-relaxed [&_li]:text-muted-foreground [&_strong]:text-foreground","children":[["$","h2","h2-0",{"className":"text-2xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-foreground mt-12 mb-4","style":{"fontFamily":"var(--font-montserrat), sans-serif"},"children":"The Short Answer"}],"\n",["$","p","p-0",{"className":"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed mb-4","children":"Funding rate farming works. The alpha is real — cross-exchange rate spreads routinely hit 20-100%+ annualized on individual pairs. But doing it manually means watching dozens of exchanges, calculating spreads, executing both legs of a hedge within seconds, managing margin across venues, and rotating when rates shift. Funding rates settle every 8 hours. Markets don't sleep. You do."}],"\n",["$","p","p-1",{"className":"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed mb-4","children":"Zirodelta's Beta-X1 engine automates the entire cycle: scan → identify → execute → monitor → rotate → distribute. Every 15 minutes across 19+ exchanges. 24/7. No human in the loop."}],"\n",["$","h2","h2-1",{"className":"text-2xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-foreground mt-12 mb-4","style":{"fontFamily":"var(--font-montserrat), sans-serif"},"children":"Why Manual Funding Rate Farming Breaks"}],"\n",["$","h3","h3-0",{"className":"text-lg font-bold text-foreground mt-8 mb-3","style":{"fontFamily":"var(--font-montserrat), sans-serif"},"children":"The Math Problem"}],"\n",["$","p","p-2",{"className":"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed mb-4","children":"Funding rates are published across 19+ major exchanges, on thousands of trading pairs, resettling every 8 hours. To find the best cross-exchange spreads, you need to:"}],"\n",["$","ol","ol-0",{"className":"space-y-2 mb-4 ml-4 list-decimal","children":["\n",["$","li","li-0",{"className":"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed","children":"Pull rates from every exchange simultaneously"}],"\n",["$","li","li-1",{"className":"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed","children":"Match pairs across venues (same asset, different exchange)"}],"\n",["$","li","li-2",{"className":"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed","children":"Compute the delta (difference between venues)"}],"\n",["$","li","li-3",{"className":"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed","children":"Rank by profitability, adjusting for liquidity, margin requirements, and fees"}],"\n",["$","li","li-4",{"className":"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed","children":"Execute both legs of the hedge within seconds"}],"\n",["$","li","li-5",{"className":"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed","children":"Repeat every 8 hours, minimum"}],"\n"]}],"\n",["$","p","p-3",{"className":"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed mb-4","children":"That's 19 exchanges × hundreds of pairs × 3 settlements per day = tens of thousands of data points daily. No human can process this in real time."}],"\n",["$","h3","h3-1",{"className":"text-lg font-bold text-foreground mt-8 mb-3","style":{"fontFamily":"var(--font-montserrat), sans-serif"},"children":"The Timing Problem"}],"\n",["$","p","p-4",{"className":"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed mb-4","children":"The best spreads appear and disappear in minutes. A pair showing 80% annualized delta at settlement might compress to 5% within an hour. If you're asleep, at dinner, or just not looking at the right pair — you miss it."}],"\n",["$","p","p-5",{"className":"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed mb-4","children":"Funding rate farming is a game of coverage: how many pairs can you monitor, how fast can you execute, and how consistently can you capture settlements. Humans cap out at watching 2-3 exchanges and a handful of pairs."}],"\n","$L9","\n","$La","\n","$Lb","\n","$Lc","\n","$Ld","\n","$Le","\n","$Lf","\n","$L10","\n","$L11","\n","$L12","\n","$L13","\n","$L14","\n","$L15","\n","$L16","\n","$L17","\n","$L18","\n","$L19","\n","$L1a","\n","$L1b","\n","$L1c","\n","$L1d","\n","$L1e","\n","$L1f","\n","$L20","\n","$L21","\n","$L22","\n","$L23","\n","$L24","\n","$L25","\n","$L26","\n","$L27","\n","$L28","\n","$L29","\n","$L2a","\n","$L2b","\n","$L2c","\n","$L2d","\n","$L2e","\n","$L2f","\n","$L30","\n","$L31","\n","$L32"]}]
