2b:["$","ul","ul-6",{"className":"space-y-2 mb-4 ml-4","children":["\n",["$","li","li-0",{"className":"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed","children":[["$","strong","strong-0",{"className":"text-foreground font-semibold","children":"Exchange risk remains."}]," Capital lives on exchanges. Automation doesn't prevent exchange insolvency. Diversification across 19+ venues is the mitigation, not elimination."]}],"\n",["$","li","li-1",{"className":"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed","children":[["$","strong","strong-0",{"className":"text-foreground font-semibold","children":"Spread compression in calm markets."}]," Low volatility means lower rate dispersion. The engine can't create spreads that don't exist. Returns are variable."]}],"\n",["$","li","li-2",{"className":"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed","children":[["$","strong","strong-0",{"className":"text-foreground font-semibold","children":"Smart contract and infrastructure risk."}]," The engine itself is software. Bugs, downtime, and connectivity issues are real operational risks. (This is why Zirodelta publishes a transparency dashboard — so you can see exactly what the engine is doing.)"]}],"\n",["$","li","li-3",{"className":"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed","children":[["$","strong","strong-0",{"className":"text-foreground font-semibold","children":"Collateral reflexivity."}]," $ZDLT price affects collateral value, which affects deployed capital, which affects revenue. The auto-deleverage system protects depositors, but the relationship exists."]}],"\n"]}]
