2d:["$","p","p-21",{"className":"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed mb-4","children":"Funding rate arbitrage is one of the few genuinely market-neutral yield strategies in crypto. The alpha comes from a structural feature of perpetual futures markets — the funding rate mechanism — that will exist as long as perps exist."}]
